To embed the keyword research tool in any website, follow these steps:

First, deploy your keyword research tool to a hosting service (like Netlify or Vercel).

Add this script to your website's HTML:



<!-- Add to your <head> or before </body> -->
<script src="https://your-deployed-url.com/embed.js"></script>

<!-- Add where you want the tool to appear -->
<div id="keyword-tool-container"></div>

<script>
  // Initialize the tool
  initKeywordTool('keyword-tool-container');
</script>




Alternative embed using iframe directly:

<iframe
  src="https://your-deployed-url.com"
  style="width: 100%; height: 800px; border: none; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);"
  title="Keyword Research Tool"
></iframe>
